  • Uses of BitSet in com.shouldis.bitset

    Subclasses of BitSet in com.shouldis.bitset 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  ConcurrentBitSet
    Implementation of BitSet in which all methods capable of reading or writing the state of bits such as ConcurrentBitSet.setWord(int, long), ConcurrentBitSet.andWord(int, long), ConcurrentBitSet.orWord(int, long), ConcurrentBitSet.xOrWord(int, long) are delegated to atomic-operations.
